; Coverage test for op.cc
; Tests the error context added when a function call throws an error.
; The calc_call method catches exceptions and adds context about which
; function was being called.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food              $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --display 'to_int(account)' -> 1
__ERROR__
While evaluating value expression:
  to_int(account)
  ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
While converting Expenses:Food:
While calling function 'to_int Expenses:Food':
While handling posting from "$FILE", line 7:
>     Expenses:Food              $50.00
Error: Cannot convert a string to an integer
end test
